main event: Observer sighted three lights side by side in New Orleans, LA on March 23, 1966, appearing round like a saucer and blinking on the edges.
interesting points: The sighting lasted between 30 seconds to 1 minute., The observer reported no sound from the objects., The observed lights were moving from west to east., The objects could have been mistaken for a 727 Whisper Jet., This event was documented in Project Blue Book, which was a USAF program for investigating UFOs.
sighted object: three round lights side by side
witness description: Kathryn Boyle, a middle-aged housewife from New Orleans
